27 (4) “Eligible individual” has the same meaning as contained in section 529A of the Internal Re-
28 venue Code.
29 (5) “Internal Revenue Code” means the federal Internal Revenue Code as amended and in effect
30 on December 31, [2023] 2025.
31 (6) “Qualified disability expense” has the same meaning as contained in section 529A of the
