38 number of years of retirement credit attributable to service in a hazardous position.
39 (c) For service as other than a police officer or firefighter or in a hazardous position, 1.5 percent
40 of final average salary multiplied by the number of years of retirement credit attributable to service
41 as other than a police officer or firefighter or in a hazardous position.
