40 of the taxpayer shall be made for Oregon tax purposes.
41 (b) The amount, if any, by which the following attributes are reduced under section 108(b)(1) of
42 the Internal Revenue Code for federal tax purposes shall be added back for Oregon tax purposes:
43 (A) Federal net operating loss.
